dialogues.dialogue:
Nanjo:  Now what?{nl}
{ctl0f:01}, do you still want{nl}
to look around the museum?{waitkey}

Yukino:  Here's the Shrine.{clearbox}It says, "Come into the{nl}
Shrine to find rest in your{nl}
soul in this busy world."{waitkey}

Maki:...{wait_fr:2000}{nl}
This Shrine looks cool!{nl}
We should come more often!{waitkey}

Elly:  This place is part of{nl}
history and we can't get in?{clearbox}I wouldn't care if there were{nl}
only rocks to see.{nl}
It's a shame we can't visit.{waitkey}

Yukino:  Wait up, {ctl0f:01}!{nl}
Are you planning to run away?{clearbox}Ms. Smith won't be happy{nl}
when she finds out!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  {ctl0f:01}...{wait_fr:2000}{nl}
You're running away?{nl}
Running won't solve anything.{waitkey}

Nanjo:  This is what I was{nl}
afraid of...{nl}
Nobody can leave this town!{waitkey}

Elly:  You can't do that,{nl}
{ctl07:01}!{clearbox}We have to take Nancy to{nl}
the school!  Quickly!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  {ctl0f:01}{nl}
This is the police station?{nl}
Your face is joke enough!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  {ctl0f:01}{nl}
We can't have any business{nl}
in a filthy place like this.{waitkey}

Yukino:  {ctl0f:01}!{nl}
You really love to wander off, don't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}But pick your time and place!{nl}
Honestly...{waitkey}

Man in black:  Beyond here is{nl}
under Sebec's control!{nl}
Passage is forbidden!{waitkey}

Maki:  What, so high and mighty!{nl}
Ugh, he really ticks me off!{nl}
Come on, everyone!  Hmph!{waitkey}

Maki:  ...{wait_fr:3c00}Aha!  Yeah,{nl}
I'm starting to feel that way!{nl}
Come on, let's hurry!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  Hey  {ctl0f:01}!  This{nl}
isn't the Police Station.{nl}
Stop fooling around!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  Hey {ctl0f:01}!{nl}
You don't have any business{nl}
in a dump like this, do you?{waitkey}

Maki:  {ctl07:01}, did the{nl}
Police Station ever look{nl}
like this?{waitkey}

Yukino:  Who the heck do they{nl}
think they are, {ctl0f:01}?{nl}
Come on, I'm leaving!{waitkey}

Maki:  What?  Just who do{nl}
they think they are?{nl}
Let's get out of here!{waitkey}

Maki:  This is strange...{nl}
Wasn't this the castle?{clearbox}We're not supposed to be able{nl}
to come here.{waitkey}

Maki:...{wait_fr:3c00}Maybe you're right!{nl}
Yes, you've got to be!{nl}
Let's go, let's go!{waitkey}

Maki:  Do you want to go to{nl}
a different place?{nl}
Wait till we're all reunited.{waitkey}

Maki:  This used to be a{nl}
flower garden.{clearbox}Since it became a forest,{nl}
no one can enter here.{waitkey}

Maki:  That little girl is{nl}
going to be all right.{nl}
Come on, let's go!{waitkey}

Nanjo: What're you going to do{nl}
when we get out of town?{nl}
We must go to the hospital!{waitkey}

Yukino:  {ctl0f:01}〔d7〕{nl}
You're irritating me!{nl}
What's with you?{waitkey}{nl}
Why're we going out of town?{waitkey}

Nanjo:  {ctl0f:01}...{nl}
What're we doing at school?{clearbox}Guido is on the east side{nl}
of town!{waitkey}

Maki:  What's happening?  The{nl}
whole school has disappeared!{nl}
What about T.J. and everybody?

Nanjo:  This, too, is caused{nl}
by the Deva System....{nl}
That Guido, I'll get him!{waitkey}

Nanjo:  Deva System...{wait_fr:5800}{nl}
But, is this what Guido{nl}
really wants to happen?{clearbox}For what reason?{nl}
This is becoming more than{nl}
what we can handle.{waitkey}

Nanjo:  {ctl0f:01}!{nl}
I was wondering...{nl}
You're not afraid, are you?{clearbox}If we don't stop Guido soon,{nl}
things will only get worse!{nl}
Now, let's go to Sebec!{waitkey}
